In the INTEREST OF S.W., Minor Child, P.W., Father, Appellant, H.W., Mother, Appellant. No. 18-1767 Court of Appeals of Iowa. Filed December 19, 2018

DECISION WITHOUT PUBLISHED OPINION

The mother and father appeal the termination of their parental rights to their child. AFFIRMED ON BOTH APPEALS.

AFFIRMED ON BOTH APPEALS.
